# floor — names only, no values (the credential interface is declarative).
# Everything here is OPTIONAL: unset means that signal is absent from the
# floor, which stays fully functional on registry + container status alone.
#
# FLOOR_GIT_TOKEN            read-only Forgejo token (assistant-grade: read
#                            repository + issues). Lights up commit / PR /
#                            issue couriers between the agent bay and the
#                            archive.
# FLOOR_AGENT_LLM_KEY        the resident agent's budgeted LiteLLM virtual
#                            key — used ONLY for /key/info self-report
#                            (spend deltas animate the reactor).
# FLOOR_ASSISTANT_LLM_KEY    same, for the assistant tenant.
# FLOOR_NODE_CONFIG_REPO     default operator/node-config
# FLOOR_COORDINATION_REPO    default operator/coordination
